    "description": "Recomm Co., Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, leases and sells information and communication equipment in Japan, China, India, and the ASEAN region. It operates through Domestic Solutions Business, Overseas Solution Business, and Business Process Re-Engineering (BPR) Business segments. The company engages in the sale of LED lighting; commercial air conditioners; SPACECOOL radioactive cooling materials; business phones; digital multifunction machines, such as copiers, printers, image scanners, and fax machines; energy-saving equipment; RoboWorker; UTM integration threatening control systems, MSG mail security, AI servers, and security endpoint products; virus sterilization equipment; robotic process automation products; other IT equipment; and telecommunications equipment. It also provides installation and maintenance services. In addition, the company offers outsourcing services for clients; business reform proposal consulting services; and contract management services. The company was formerly known as RECOMM Holdings Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Recomm Co., Ltd. in June 2013. Recomm Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 1994 and is headquartered in Shibuya, Japan."
